    public static final String Gal_5_21 = "Envyings, murders, drunkenness, revellings, and such like: of the which I tell you before, as I have also told [you] in time past, that they which do such things shall not inherit the kingdom of God. ";
    public static final String Gal_5_22 = "But the fruit of the Spirit is love, joy, peace, longsuffering, gentleness, goodness, faith, ";
